rdfs:label: euro
dc:description: The official currency of a large subset of member countries of the European Union.

rdfs:label: point
dc:description: An arbitrary unit of value, usually an integer indicating reward or penalty.

rdfs:label: uV
dc:description: Added as a direct unit because it is the default unit.

rdfs:label: dB
dc:description: Intensity expressed as ratio to a threshold. May be used for sound intensity.

rdfs:label: candela
dc:description: Units used to express light intensity.

rdfs:label: cd
dc:description: Units used to express light intensity.

rdfs:label: degree Celsius
dc:description: Units are not allowed to have spaces. Use degree-Celsius or oC.

rdfs:label: year
dc:description: Years do not have a constant conversion factor to seconds.
